      "html": "<h4>Cool Down Activity</h4>\n<p>Acetaminophen is a common pain reliever and fever reducer. Here is a graph showing the amount of acetaminophen, in milligrams, in an adult&rsquo;s body at different times after they take a normal dose.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Graph of an exponential function, origin O. time (hours) and acetaminophen (mg).\" src=\"https://k12.openstax.org/contents/raise/resources/6067169e5114ec7c6decefb23c92843d3d582b07\"></p>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol>\n      <li>Answer the following questions.\n        <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" type=\"a\">\n          <li> What is the vertical intercept?</li>\n        </ol>\n      </li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p> 1,000 </p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol>\n      <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"2\" type=\"a\">\n        <li> What does it mean in this situation?</li>\n      </ol>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p>There are 1,000 mg of acetaminophen in the person&rsquo;s body after taking the medicine (this is the dose size). </p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"2\">\n      <li> What fraction of the medicine remained after one hour? </li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p>\\(\\frac34\\) of the medicine remained after 1 hour since \\(\\frac{750}{1000}=\\frac{3}{4}\\). </p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"Reveal1\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"3\">\n      <li> Write an equation that represents the amount of medicine, \\(a\\), after \\(t\\) hours. </li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-prompt\">\n    <p>Write down your answer, then select the <strong>Solution</strong> button to compare your work.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-content\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"Reveal1\">\n  <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n  <p> \\(a=1,000(\\frac{3}{4})^t\\) </p>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->"
    }
  ]
}